import { Navbar, Col, Nav, Form, FormControl, Button, Container } from 'react-bootstrap';
import { FaSearch } from 'react-icons/fa';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';


export default function Header () {
    return (
        <Container fluid='false' className='header-bg'>
            <Container className='navbar'>
                <Col>
                    <Link to='/'>
                        Movie
                    </Link>
                </Col>
                    
                    <Form inline className="search-form d-flex w-100">
                        <FormControl 
                            type="text"
                            placeholder="Search"
                            className="w-100"
                        />
                        <Button type="submit">
                            <FaSearch />
                        </Button>
                    </Form>
                    <Nav.Link className="signin">Sign in</Nav.Link>          
                
            </Container>
        </Container>
    )
}
